via xkb patch use BackSpace with Alt+Shift modifier to insert substitute for && and BackSlash with
Alt+Shift modifier to insert substitute for || (characters from extended character set - see Appendix C of TeXbook), BackSpace with Alt modifier is free and may be used for something else; and uncomment "\let\K=\leftarrow" in cwebmaX.tex
